body:
Since a lot of people are making a thread full of their collective Youtube videos, I thought I would do the same. ;) Mostly what my channel is comprised of is Creative Building, Let's Builds, and Modded MC. However, I want to start recording some PvP gameplay and most preferably cinematics of maps. Enjoy fools!
